	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Fast. Cupr., Degrassi 244f.; Fast. Ven., ibid. 251, 254f.; Fast. Mag. Vic., ibid. 283, 288; Fast. Amit., ibid. 170f.; cf. ibid. 136, 5101.; on Cornelius, see PIR² 2.308, no. 1313, and 314, no. 1338; De Laet no. 126; on Valerius, see PIR 3.370, no. 94; De Laet no. 399." .
